									<UML:ModelElement.taggedValue>
										<UML:TaggedValue tag="documentation" value="The Geologic Time package, developed by Simon Cox (CSIRO) and Steve Richard (Arizona Geological Survey), contains elements used to describe the classification of geologic time: time periods, time boundaries, and the relationships between them as defined by the IUGS International Commission on Stratigraphy (ICS - http://www.stratigraphy.org/). &#xA;"/>
