											</UML:ModelElement.stereotype>
											<UML:ModelElement.taggedValue>
												<UML:TaggedValue tag="documentation" value="&lt;font color=&quot;#4f81bd&quot;&gt;ContactView&lt;/font&gt; is a simplified view of a GeoSciML &lt;font color=&quot;#4f81bd&quot;&gt;MappedFeature&lt;/font&gt; with key property values from an associated &lt;font color=&quot;#4f81bd&quot;&gt;Contact&lt;/font&gt; feature.  These properties are summarised as labels (unconstrained character strings) or arbitrarily selected classifiers to be used for thematic mapping purposes. The latter are the properties suffixed with “_uri” and will contain URIs referring to controlled concepts in published vocabularies.&#xA;"/>
