													</UML:ModelElement.stereotype>
													<UML:ModelElement.taggedValue>
														<UML:TaggedValue tag="documentation" value="The Geomorphology sub-package describes features that comprise the shape and nature of the Earth's land surface (i.e., landforms).  These landforms may be created by natural or anthropogenic processes.&#xA;"/>
