																<UML:TaggedValue tag="description" value="The geologicHistory is an association that relates one or more GeologicEvents to a GeologicFeature to describe their age or geologic history.  Normally, GeoSciML uses the generic relatedFeature::GeologicRelation to associate GeologicFeature with other GeologicFeatures, including GeologicEvent.  However, this design was deemed too complex for GeoSciML Basic and is therefore only available from the GeoSciML Extension package.  "/>
