															</UML:StructuralFeature.type>
															<UML:ModelElement.taggedValue>
																<UML:TaggedValue tag="description" value="The &lt;font color=&quot;#4f81bd&quot;&gt;purpose:DescriptionPurpose&lt;/font&gt; property provides a specification of the intended purpose or level of abstraction for the given &lt;font color=&quot;#4f81bd&quot;&gt;EarthMaterial&lt;/font&gt;. The intent is the same a &lt;font color=&quot;#4f81bd&quot;&gt;GeologicFeature&lt;/font&gt;’s purpose and it shares the same vocabulary (instance, typicalNorm, definingNorm).&#xA;"/>
