															<UML:ModelElement.taggedValue>
																<UML:TaggedValue tag="description" value="The property hierarchyLink is an association that links a GeologicUnit with a GeologicUnitHierarchy  to represent containment of a part GeologicUnit within another GeologicUnit. It indicates a subsidiary unit with its role and proportion with respect to the container unit.  For example, members are described as part of formations, or different facies can be described as parts of a GeologicUnit."/>
