											</UML:ModelElement.stereotype>
											<UML:ModelElement.taggedValue>
												<UML:TaggedValue tag="documentation" value="This class is an indicative placeholder only for a vocabulary of terms describing the borehole drilling method.  Users are encouraged to use a vocabulary of terms managed by the CGI vocabularies working group. (eg; auger, hand auger, air core, cable tool, diamond core, rotary air blast, etc)"/>
