															<UML:ModelElement.taggedValue>
																<UML:TaggedValue tag="description" value="The property sourceCollection is an association between a GeochronologicInterpretation and an OM::SF_SamplingFeatureCollection that lists a collection of OM::SF_SamplingFeature (e.g., a collection of burn spots or craters from a SHRIMP analytical session).  When legacy published data for which the SamplingFeatureCollection is unknown, it may be delivered with SamplingFeatureCollection = 'unknown'."/>
